<template>
   <vue-tree-nav
    :left="left"
    :right="right"
  ></vue-tree-nav>
</template>

<script>
 import treeNav from 'vue-tree-nav'
export default {
    name: 'vue-tree-nav',
    components: {
      'item': item,
      'vue-over-body': overBody
    },
    props: {
      side: {
        type: Array,
        default: () => []
      },
      left: {
        type: Array,
        default: () => []
      },
      right: {
        type: Array,
        default: () => []
      },
      location: {
        type: String,
        default: ''
      },
      showPath: {
        type: Boolean,
        default: true 
      },
      barScale: {
        type: Number,
        default: 1
      },
      sideScale: {
        type: Number,
        default: 1
      },
      bgColor: {
        type: String,
        default: '#f3f3f3'
      },
      fontColor: {
        type: String,
        default: '#666666'
      },
      hoverColor: {
        type: String,
        default: '#dddddd'
      },
      activeColor: {
        type: String,
        default: '#000000'
      }
    }}
</script>

<style>

</style>
